            <li>Passwords are hashed and never stored in plain text</li>
            <li>Access to data is protected by authentication and row-level security policies</li>
        </ul>
        <p>While we implement safeguards to protect your information, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
